 do século 17 descobriu interação entre animais 400 anos antes dos cientistas" title="Quadro do século 17 descobriu interação entre animais 400 anos antes dos cientistas" srcSet="https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/KzWv7E07hOITQwqTRiqCXXQpAjc=/540x304/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/7/V/FHFsMOQIusOP93ohg6jg/image2.png 1x,https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/CFWzhDojLeiPqwpfWdi2YBuRDxk=/810x456/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/7/V/FHFsMOQIusOP93ohg6jg/image2.png 1.5x,https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/IFHcucyX0uS7304I5aYW2XB-StM=/1080x608/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/7/V/FHFsMOQIusOP93ohg6jg/image2.png 2x" src="https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/KzWv7E07hOITQwqTRiqCXXQpAjc=/540x304/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/7/V/FHFsMOQIusOP93ohg6jg/image2.png" elementtiming="image-ssr" loading="lazy" /></picture></div></a></div></div><div class="feed-post-metadata"><span class="feed-post-datetime">Há 19 horas</span><span class="feed-post-metadata-section"> Ciência </span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bstn-err-container"><div class="bastian-feed-item" data-index="6"><div class="feed-post bstn-item-shape type-materia"><div class="feed-post-body"><div class="feed-post-header"></div><div class="_label_event"><div class="feed-post-body-title gui-color-primary gui-color-hover "><div class="_re"><h2 class="feed-post-link gui-color-primary gui-color-hover"><a href="https://revistagalileu.globo.com/ciencia/biologia/noticia/2026/07/esta-aranha-quebrou-o-recorde-de-mais-rapida-do-mundo.ghtml" class="feed-post-link" elementtiming="text-ssr">Esta aranha quebrou o recorde de mais rápida do mundo</a></h2></div></div></div><div class="_label_event"><p class="feed-post-body-resumo" elementtiming="text-ssr">Estudo analisou mais de 160 espécies de aranhas e concluiu que pernas relativamente longas, e não apenas o tamanho do corpo, ajudam a explicar quais aranhas são melhores na corrida</p></div><div class="feed-media-wrapper"><div class="_label_event"><a href="https://revistagalileu.globo.com/ciencia/biologia/noticia/2026/07/esta-aranha-quebrou-o-recorde-de-mais-rapida-do-mundo.ghtml" class="feed-post-figure-link gui-image-hover"><div class="bstn-fd-item-cover "><picture class="bstn-fd-cover-picture"><img class="bstn-fd-picture-image" alt="Esta aranha quebrou o recorde de mais rápida do mundo" title="Esta aranha quebrou o recorde de mais rápida do mundo" srcSet="https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/WHbum3QGrJb3USdtH7yDjKHCrxo=/540x304/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/D/K/7kZtIdSRCTlXEkVxSFSg/sei-303478410.webp 1x,https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/vAVZ-wpBa4EgcarI92KcO7ZBANs=/810x456/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/D/K/7kZtIdSRCTlXEkVxSFSg/sei-303478410.webp 1.5x,https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/rXBLiE0EOABC_LuyNSftlkvRHlU=/1080x608/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/D/K/7kZtIdSRCTlXEkVxSFSg/sei-303478410.webp 2x" src="https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/WHbum3QGrJb3USdtH7yDjKHCrxo=/540x304/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/D/K/7kZtIdSRCTlXEkVxSFSg/sei-303478410.webp" elementtiming="image-ssr" loading="lazy" /></picture></div></a></div></div><div class="feed-post-metadata"><span class="feed-post-datetime">Há 20 horas</span><span class="feed-post-metadata-section"> Biologia </span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bstn-err-container"><div class="bastian-feed-item" data-index="7"><div class="feed-post bstn-item-shape type-materia"><div class="feed-post-body"><div class="feed-post-header"></div><div class="_label_event"><div class="feed-post-body-title gui-color-primary gui-color-hover "><div class="_re"><h2 class="feed-post-link gui-color-primary gui-color-hover"><a href="https://revistagalileu.globo.com/ciencia/biologia/noticia/2026/07/este-caranguejo-sobreviveu-a-deriva-dentro-de-uma-garrafa-por-2-meses.ghtml" class="feed-post-link" elementtiming="text-ssr">Este caranguejo sobreviveu à deriva dentro de uma garrafa por 2 meses</a></h2></div></div></div><div class="_label_event"><p class="feed-post-body-resumo" elementtiming="text-ssr">Após entrar em um recipiente plástico, crustáceo cresceu até ficar grande demais para conseguir sair; conheça a história</p></div><div class="feed-media-wrapper"><div class="_label_event"><a href="https://revistagalileu.globo.com/ciencia/biologia/noticia/2026/07/este-caranguejo-sobreviveu-a-deriva-dentro-de-uma-garrafa-por-2-meses.ghtml" class="feed-post-figure-link gui-image-hover"><div class="bstn-fd-item-cover "><picture class="bstn-fd-cover-picture"><img class="bstn-fd-picture-image" alt="Este caranguejo sobreviveu à deriva dentro de uma garrafa por 2 meses" title="Este caranguejo sobreviveu à deriva dentro de uma garrafa por 2 meses" srcSet="https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/lLO4jHDOy4C5WyZz37CCuTZrN1g=/540x304/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/S/z/ldLBPkQYqqQBLNaAt5fw/low-res-fig2.jpg 1x,https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/TZuBG_PE6JzcEZmEWAV-tGGBpfw=/810x456/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/S/z/ldLBPkQYqqQBLNaAt5fw/low-res-fig2.jpg 1.5x,https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/q9GgSbEXxgxygwyPT22Bnka2gYw=/1080x608/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/S/z/ldLBPkQYqqQBLNaAt5fw/low-res-fig2.jpg 2x" src="https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/lLO4jHDOy4C5WyZz37CCuTZrN1g=/540x304/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/S/z/ldLBPkQYqqQBLNaAt5fw/low-res-fig2.jpg" elementtiming="image-ssr" loading="lazy" /></picture></div></a></div></div><div class="feed-post-metadata"><span class="feed-post-datetime">Há 20 horas</span><span class="feed-post-metadata-section"> Biologia </span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bstn-err-container"><div class="bastian-feed-item" data-index="8"><div class="feed-post bstn-item-shape type-materia"><div class="feed-post-body"><div class="feed-post-header"></div><div class="_label_event"><div class="feed-post-body-title gui-color-primary gui-color-hover "><div class="_re"><h2 class="feed-post-link gui-color-primary gui-color-hover"><a href="https://revistagalileu.globo.com/ciencia/espaco/noticia/2026/07/maior-camera-digital-do-mundo-comeca-operar-e-faz-registros-detalhados-do-espaco.ghtml" class="feed-post-link" elementtiming="text-ssr">Maior câmera digital do mundo começa operar e faz registros detalhados do espaço</a></h2></div></div></div><div class="_label_event"><p class="feed-post-body-resumo" elementtiming="text-ssr">Instalada no Chile, estrutura inicia um levantamento inédito que acompanhará bilhões de corpos celestes por dez anos e poderá transformar o conhecimento científico sobre a evolução do Universo</p></div><div class="feed-media-wrapper"><div class="_label_event"><a href="https://revistagalileu.globo.com/ciencia/espaco/noticia/2026/07/maior-camera-digital-do-mundo-comeca-operar-e-faz-registros-detalhados-do-espaco.ghtml" class="feed-post-figure-link gui-image-hover"><div class="bstn-fd-item-cover "><picture class="bstn-fd-cover-picture"><img class="bstn-fd-picture-image" alt="Maior câmera digital do mundo começa operar e faz registros detalhados do espaço" title="Maior câmera digital do mundo começa operar e faz registros detalhados do espaço" srcSet="https://s2-galileu.glbimg.com/PTnqJKRElOa_h3qr_aM5gVN3_vg=/540x304/top/smart/https://i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_fde5cd494fb04473a83fa5fd57ad4542/internal_photos/bs/2026/w/A/LMC9EIQVSztCHVw5e98A/frame1frame7-blended-fused.jpg 1x,https://s2-ga